<author>lǚ xiǎo mǐn</author>
<title>píng yuán hé gāo shān 迦南1149</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 píng yuán hé gāo shān zài nǐ yǎn qián, wèn nǐ yào wǎng nǎ biān.
 píng yuán suī píng tǎn shén bù xǐ huān. zài nà lǐ jìn bù le jiā nán.
 shàng shān suī jiān nán, zhǔ què zài shān diān. gěi nǐ zhǐ chū huí jiā de lù xiàn.
 yà bó lā hǎn pān dēng gāo gāo de shān, luō dé jiǎn xuǎn quán píng yuán.
 rén shēng zhī lù shàng, yǒu tài duō de jiǎn xuǎn, chà zhī háo lí miù zhī qiān lǐ yuǎn.
 píng yuán hé gāo shān zài nǐ yǎn qián, wèn nǐ jiǎn xuǎn nǎ yī biān.</lyrics>
</song>